data.description: Step right into this delightful 3 bed / 2.5 bath gem nestled in Captain's Cove, a golfing community that's truly picturesque. This modern beauty features soaring cathedral ceilings, gleaming stainless steel appliances, a dreamy walk-in closet, and a cozy rear deck, perfect for sipping sweet tea. But that's not all! Luxuriate in the whirlpool tub, stay warm by the pellet stove on chilly nights, and keep your cars snug in the 2-car garage. Living in the Cove comes with perks like THREE sparkling pools, a fitness center, a marina for water adventures, a serene library, and courts for sports enthusiasts, 24/7 security for peace of mind, and so much more!  Don't let this paradise slip away. It's time to make your dream home in the Cove a reality!
